pda.datas

Class ParamDatas

  • java.lang.Object
    • pda.datas.ParamDatas

  • public class ParamDatas
extends java.lang.Object
    ParamDatas is a class containing all the parameters of the Photoboost application It save and load the parameters on a "parametres.out" file.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Florent Catiau-Tristant and Mehdi Haddad
